<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to the Coding Hub</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&family=Orbitron:wght@500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* Modern CSS Reset & CSS Variables */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-color: #0d0e15;
            --card-bg: #161925;
            --text-main: #f3f4f6;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --neon-cyan: #00f2fe;
            --neon-purple: #4facfe;
            --glow-shadow: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.2);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Subtle background ambient glow elements */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: -10%;
            left: -10%;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: -10%;
            right: -10%;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        /* Centered Main Container */
        .container {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-top: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 30px var(--glow-shadow);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 0 40px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.3);
        }

        /* Header Style */
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--neon-cyan) 0%, var(--neon-purple) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Intro Paragraph */
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Stylized Action Badge (Optional visual polish) */
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--neon-cyan);
            color: var(--neon-cyan);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Footer Style */
        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 2rem 1rem 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* Responsive scaling */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            p { font-size: 1rem; }
            .container { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">System Online</div>
        <h1>Welcome to [YOUR SITE NAME]</h1>
        
        <p>
            This is my master coding hub. A centralized command center built to host my web applications, experiment with cutting-edge tech stacks, and showcase my development journey. Stay tuned as future modules deploy.
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        Created by [YOUR NAME] in 2026
    </footer>

</body>
</html>